{"tid":217974,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家去過邊間仆街嘅診所","createTime":"2017-04-26T07:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T08:40:11.000Z","uid":72391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61f4377ae8ddc94e5b777a07b9b706174b9ed815","tid":217974,"uid":72391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"今日陪女朋友去打9合1疫苗第二針<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/26/152904_c5c7b876d09670217bc1afd1d6d43a58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F26%2F152904_c5c7b876d09670217bc1afd1d6d43a58.jpg&h=96954feb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一早已經預約好今日打，佢叫我地早d去驚唔夠針打<br />\n我同女朋友朝早十點就去到銅鑼灣依間診所<br />\n<br />\n個經理一出黎就屈我地冇預約<br />\n然後就話冇曬針<br />\n明明打第一針嗰陣已經俾曬$4000,你診所梗係有責任要喺期限內幫客人打針<br />\n而家就推卸責任話美國個廠問題<br />\n船期未到，俾兩個選擇一係要打嘅話可以帶你去相熟醫生度打不過要收你$350,一係就等佢船期到不過唔定5月尾定6月，然後就嚇你話俾3分鐘你決定<br />\n你冇留疫苗俾客責任完全喺診所度，有乜理由仲要客人額外俾錢去彌補你嘅錯誤<br />\n你同我講全港冇曬疫苗唔緊要，同我say個sorry我接受<br />\n但你有解決方法你又唔解決，要客自己去俾錢<br />\n搞足半日一句sorry都冇，仲講到好似我地錯咁<br />\n<br />\n我眼見已經幾個客唔想等，直接俾錢黑店帶佢去相熟診所打針<br />\n有d客唔肯再額外俾錢，間黑店仲屈埋d中介幫客俾"},{"pid":"05b5f092b86b820b946ebd97a8b48aed3a92420a","tid":217974,"uid":4175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:33:56.000Z","msg":"其實打針唔應該一次過俾曬三針錢"},{"pid":"68060f2f1f97527450eb3d99adefd11ac99422c8","tid":217974,"uid":72391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X7pA32a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX7pA32a.jpg&h=9728bc95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/26/153007_c5de43fc575f699648f14df65e7ec252.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F26%2F153007_c5de43fc575f699648f14df65e7ec252.jpg&h=df25e298&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a453bfb3fb2c68d3c4bc16cf28b733aecaed5f6","tid":217974,"uid":72391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X7pA32a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX7pA32a.jpg&h=9728bc95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/26/153007_c5de43fc575f699648f14df65e7ec252.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F26%2F153007_c5de43fc575f699648f14df65e7ec252.jpg&h=df25e298&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係依個肥婆經理，不停推卸責任之餘仲理直氣壯，態度極差，又眼睥睥"},{"pid":"55ba96e186b9325d97f3678d2c3d7a51d486ae13","tid":217974,"uid":8167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:47:14.000Z","msg":"點解打呢隻針 係咪預防癌 同性病"},{"pid":"a72a6932a342cd946b6c5fb3e2c6d53c5d5bf8be","tid":217974,"uid":72391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:50:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解打呢隻針 係咪預防癌 同性病</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3XY7u6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3XY7u6.jpg&h=1f3495a0&s={SIZE}\" />癌同椰菜花"},{"pid":"f148f8a9dfc5fbeddf74803fc01ce3143e408fb4","tid":217974,"uid":72391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:55:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實打針唔應該一次過俾曬三針錢</blockquote><br />\n但佢係一個package黎，9合1疫苗好似出面都係一次過收曬3針錢"},{"pid":"aadb50f52d9cbdec3af2bd1b9474a04a7f78a881","tid":217974,"uid":64680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"無知一問，可唔可以去海關告佢？"},{"pid":"2b92843b5b1ad79233a7e5cf6cafd6d48bb5c167","tid":217974,"uid":72391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:19:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無知一問，可唔可以去海關告佢？</blockquote><br />\n我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個客都俾佢昆咗俾多幾百蚊出去打<br />\n本身企硬嗰幾個客都因為趕時間而俾咗錢"},{"pid":"5137bd6568196486d85e06606c7beb6088994b53","tid":217974,"uid":72391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:40:11.000Z","msg":"你話有相熟醫生可以打<br />\n咁你又唔攞疫苗翻黎幫客打<br />\n當你攞唔到疫苗<br />\n咁你帶d客去相熟醫生度打，費用點都應該係你負責啊<br />\n你俾唔到貨d客又唔通知，個個客戇鳩鳩上黎等<br />\n仲要上到黎俾你屈多幾百蚊先有得打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇佢幾時執"}]}